latestIgtvVideos.title: Not So Basic Color Combinations
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Let's talk about these 4 outfits!💁‍♀️
1) A simple gray dress with a belt is something that I would usually pair, but adding a pink top with gold details gives the overall outfit a touch of effort. Pairing the double ring belt with gold footwear(you can wear gold hoops earrings) and then pairing the black belt with black clutch has absolutely aced the look!😉
.
2) A nice blue color jumpsuit with silver details is itself chic, but by adding a pink leather jacket made it even more chic. So, it's basic yet not so basic!🙈
.
3)Okay, so when I was researching about some color combinations, they said green and pink is a no-no. It's true when you don't have the perfect blending colors, but when I saw these colors in the kurti and ghangra, I fell in love🤗
.
4) Ah, my favorite outfit. Perfect Indo-Western look. The yellow top (from @shein_in) and green flare pants(which is a pant from my another suit, from @aurelia_womenswear). The look felt a bit incomplete, so I added a brown belt(from @sheinofficial) and a pair of oxidized jewelry, and voila!!😍
.
